### Variables
# Management API runs on port 40301
# userJan ID: 20000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001

### Send hangout invite to userJan
POST http://localhost:40301/api/exchanges/%2F/zuyp.notifications/publish
Authorization: Basic guest guest
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "properties": {},
  "routing_key": "user-20000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001",
  "payload": "{\"type\":\"hangout_invite\",\"hangoutId\":\"hangout-abc123\"}",
  "payload_encoding": "string"
}

### Send zuyp alert to userJan
POST http://localhost:40301/api/exchanges/%2F/zuyp.notifications/publish
Authorization: Basic guest guest
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "properties": {},
  "routing_key": "user-20000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001",
  "payload": "{\"type\":\"zuyp_alert\",\"hangoutId\":\"hangout-abc123\"}",
  "payload_encoding": "string"
}
